 Sunday 21 April Particular quiet on the front all day . Glorious day there has been much aerial work . Our post is just under the shadow of the Mont des Cat . Two stretcher case from the line . Monday 22 April To-day has been veri hot round our Aid Post Fritz has shell us all day . He obtain one direct hit on our hous wound one chap fair bad . A veri heavi bombard on our left . I think thing will be quit warm about here in the futur .
